statements.sql: select "locations".*, "route_location"."route_id" as "pivot_route_id", "route_location"."location_id" as "pivot_location_id", "route_location"."order" as "pivot_order", "route_location"."arrival_time" as "pivot_arrival_time", "route_location"."completion_time" as "pivot_completion_time", "route_location"."travel_time" as "pivot_travel_time" from "locations" inner join "route_location" on "locations"."id" = "route_location"."location_id" where "route_location"."route_id" in (9, 10, 11, 12) order by "route_location"."order" asc
